    "The Beta channel ships every change merged to main and may be unstable. Switch back to Stable to receive only tagged releases.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Beta channel ships every change merged to main and may be unstable. Switch back to Stable to receive only tagged releases."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Beta 通道会推送合并到 main 的每次更改，可能不稳定。切换回稳定版以仅接收带标签的发布。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Muxy Picker starts in this default location. Use App Default to reset it. Projects can stay in the sidebar after closing their last tab.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy Picker starts in this default location. Use App Default to reset it. Projects can stay in the sidebar after closing their last tab."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy 选择器从此默认位置开始。使用应用默认以重置。关闭最后一个标签页后项目可以保留在侧边栏。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Muxy Picker can use Finder or Muxy's picker. Projects can stay in the sidebar after closing their last tab.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy Picker can use Finder or Muxy's picker. Projects can stay in the sidebar after closing their last tab."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy 选择器可以使用 Finder 或 Muxy 的选择器。关闭最后一个标签页后项目可以保留在侧边栏。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Muxy creates a project-named subfolder inside this folder. Projects can still override this from the new worktree dialog.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy creates a project-named subfolder inside this folder. Projects can still override this from the new worktree dialog."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muxy 会在此文件夹内创建一个以项目名命名的子文件夹。项目仍可从新工作树对话框中覆盖此设置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anonymous crash reports help us fix bugs. Reports never include project paths, file contents, or personal data.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Anonymous crash reports help us fix bugs. Reports never include project paths, file contents, or personal data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匿名崩溃报告帮助我们修复 Bug。报告中绝不包含项目路径、文件内容或个人数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Select the default folder for new worktrees": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Select the default folder for new worktrees"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "选择新工作树的默认文件夹"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Inline File Path keeps multiple images perfectly ordered with text and Enter. Use Clipboard Paste if your TUI doesn't recognize image paths.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inline File Path keeps multiple images perfectly ordered with text and Enter. Use Clipboard Paste if your TUI doesn't recognize image paths."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "内联文件路径让多张图片与文本和回车键完美对齐。如果您的 TUI 无法识别图片路径，请使用剪贴板粘贴。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Press the Voice Recording shortcut to dictate. Muxy transcribes your speech on-device and inserts it wherever your cursor was before you opened the recorder. If that target is gone, the transcript lands on your clipboard.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Press the Voice Recording shortcut to dictate. Muxy transcribes your speech on-device and inserts it wherever your cursor was before you opened the recorder. If that target is gone, the transcript lands on your clipboard."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "按下语音录制快捷键进行口述。Muxy 在设备上转录您的语音，并将其插入到打开录音器之前光标所在的位置。如果该目标已消失，转录内容将进入您的剪贴板。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No on-device speech models are installed. Add a dictation language in System Settings → Keyboard → Dictation, then return here.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No on-device speech models are installed. Add a dictation language in System Settings → Keyboard → Dictation, then return here."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "未安装设备端语音模型。请在系统设置 → 键盘 → 听写中添加听写语言，然后返回此处。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Only languages with an on-device model are listed. Transcription never leaves your Mac.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only languages with an on-device model are listed. Transcription never leaves your Mac."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅列出具有设备端模型的语言。转录绝不会离开您的 Mac。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scan this with the Muxy mobile app to add this Mac. The QR carries no token — first-time pairing still needs your approval.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Scan this with the Muxy mobile app to add this Mac. The QR carries no token — first-time pairing still needs your approval."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用 Muxy 移动应用扫描此二维码以添加此 Mac。二维码不携带任何令牌 — 首次配对仍需要您的批准。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Choose the agentic CLI tool used to generate commit messages and pull request drafts. The tool runs locally with your existing authentication.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Choose the agentic CLI tool used to generate commit messages and pull request drafts. The tool runs locally with your existing authentication."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "选择用于生成提交信息和 Pull Request 草稿的代理 CLI 工具。该工具使用您现有的认证在本地运行。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Guides the model when generating PR title and description. Output is parsed as JSON; do not change the response format.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Guides the model when generating PR title and description. Output is parsed as JSON; do not change the response format."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "指导模型生成 PR 标题和描述。输出会被解析为 JSON；请勿更改响应格式。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Runs through your interactive login shell so PATH and aliases resolve. Muxy pipes the full prompt to stdin and reads the response from stdout. Provide arguments that make the tool emit only the response (no banners or progress).": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Runs through your interactive login shell so PATH and aliases resolve. Muxy pipes the full prompt to stdin and reads the response from stdout. Provide arguments that make the tool emit only the response (no banners or progress)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通过您的交互式登录 shell 运行，因此 PATH 和别名可以解析。Muxy 将完整提示词通过管道输送到 stdin 并从 stdout 读取响应。提供参数使工具仅输出响应（无横幅或进度）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enter a port between %@ and %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Enter a port between %@ and %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请输入 %@ 到 %@ 之间的端口。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
